high_descs: Turn right, go forward a step, turn left, go forward, turn right, go forward to the wall, turn right, go forward to the trash bag, turn right to face the table.
Take the large knife next to the salt from the table.
Stay at the table.
Cut the bread on the table into slices.
Put the knife on the table to the right of the bread.
Take a slice of bread from the table.
Turn right, go forward to the fridge.
Chill the bread in the fridge on the lowest shelf. Take the bread from the bridge.
Turn around, go forward to the trash bag, turn right to the table.
Put the bread slice on the table to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of bread on a table.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the far end of the white table on the right.
Pick up the yellow knife on the table.
Move back  slightly from the table.
Slice the bread on the left on top of the table.
Place the knife back on the table.
Pick up one slice of the bread from the table.
Turn right and go to the refrigerator in front.
Remove the bread after cooling it in the refrigerator.
Turn around and go back to he white table across the room.
Place the bread slice on the table on the right side of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bread slice on the table.

high_descs: go straight, then move around the white table to the opposite side
pick up the knife with the yellow handle on the white table
face the loaf of bread on the white table
slice half of the bread on the table
place the knife on the table to the right of the bread
pick up a slice of bread from the table
turn right and move to the refrigerator on the opposite side of the room
open the refrigerator, place the bread on the second from the top shelf, close the door for several seconds, then open it again to take the slice out
go back to the white table and face the bread slices
place the slice of bread to the right of the knife on the table
anns.task_desc: slice some bread and cool it down in the refrigerator
